data.description: LOCATION! LOCATION! NO HOA! Beautiful family home in a highly desirable location, close to great schools, restaurants, shopping centers and much more.  Huge back yard, front porch and plenty of parking space! Great for entertainment, and excellent for those looking to park their boat and truck. This property offers 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms and has a remodeled kitchen and bathrooms.  Huge back yard with avocado, mango trees, and a coconut tree in the front.  Cozy, remodeled front porch waiting for you to relax in it, after a long day of work.  Impact windows in the front of the house.  Impact front door and security cameras installed outside.  One of the bedrooms has a door to the outside, if your guest wants some privacy.  Don't miss this wonderful opportunity!!!
